          "heading": "What is decentralized storage?",
          "description": "Governments and communities need accessible and cost-effective ways to store public datasets. Filecoin makes decentralized storage easy, and it costs <a href='https://file.app/'>a fraction</a> of the price of centralized cloud storage.<br><br>On the Filecoin network, files are stored on a distributed network of professional storage providers around the globe, with built-in economic incentives to ensure files are stored reliably over time. The mission of Filecoin is to create a decentralized, efficient, and robust foundation for humanity’s information. ",
          "subheading": "",
          "ctas": [
            {
              "type": "A",
              "theme": "pdc",
